### 3.4 Section 4: 12原型画廊

#### 原型卡片样式 (塔罗风格)

```css
.archetype-card {
  width: 180px;
  height: 280px;
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}

.archetype-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 8px;
  left: 8px;
  right: 8px;
  bottom: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--vellum-300);
  border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 4px);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.archetype-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
}

.archetype-card .number {
  font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--ink-400);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.archetype-card .name {
  font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  text-align: center;
