## 四、交互设计

### 4.1 滚动动画

```typescript
const SCROLL_ANIMATIONS = {
  // Section 入场动画
  sectionReveal: {
    type: 'fade-up',
    duration: 0.6,
    delay: 0.1,
    ease: 'ease-out'
  },

  // 卡片依次入场
  staggerCards: {
    type: 'fade-up',
    staggerDelay: 0.1,
    duration: 0.4
  }
}
```

### 4.2 悬浮效果 (Linear 风格)

```css
/* 卡片悬浮 - 微妙上浮 + 阴影变化 */
.card-hover {
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.card-hover:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
}

/* 按钮悬浮 */
.button-hover:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
}
```

### 4.3 微动效

```typescript
const MICRO_ANIMATIONS = {
  // VibeID 能量符号呼吸
  symbolBreathe: {
    scale: [1, 1.02, 1],
    duration: 4,
    ease: 'ease-in-out',
    repeat: Infinity
  },

  // 12原型色环旋转
  colorRingRotate: {
    rotate: 360,
    duration: 30,
    ease: 'linear',
    repeat: Infinity
  },

  // 向下箭头跳动
  scrollHint: {
    y: [0, 6, 0],
    duration: 1.5,
    ease: 'ease-in-out',
    repeat: Infinity
  }
}
```

